The evidence with the title 'US Economic Growth is over: the Short Run meets the Long Run ' says Frustrated jockey dressed in the colors of the. American flag frantically trying to get some movement from the gigantic but sluggish turtle that he is riding . U.S. real gdp growth has grown at aturtle - like pace of only 2.1 percent per year in the last four years , despite a rapid decline in the unemployment rate from 10 to 6 percent. 
